UMASIPALA weTheku ukhiphe isimemezelo wazisa ngezinhlelo zokucinywa kukagesi okuhleliwe ezindaweni ezimbalwa eThekwini. Izindawo ezihlelelwe ukucinyelwa ugesi yilezi eziphakelwa yisiteshi esiseMarianridge. Lokhu kungenxa yokuthi umasipala uhlele ukulungisa isiteshi ukuze sikwazi ukusebenza ngendlela efanelekile. Lokhu kuqala namhlanje kanti ugesi uzoze ubuye ngoLwesihlanu ekuseni ngo-3.